# 🔫 GM Samp Battle Ground

![License](https://img.shields.io/badge/license-MIT-blue.svg)
![Status](https://img.shields.io/badge/status-active-brightgreen)
![Version](https://img.shields.io/badge/version-1.0.0-orange)

**GM Samp Battle Ground** adalah mode game seru berbasis SA:MP (San Andreas Multiplayer) yang mengusung konsep pertempuran ala battle royale. Cocok buat server komunitas yang pengen nuansa kompetitif, cepat, dan intens!

---

## 🎮 Fitur Unggulan

✅ Sistem zona aman (Safe Zone) otomatis  
✅ Supply Drop & Random Weapon Spawn  
✅ Custom UI Kill Feed dan Status Player  
✅ Sistem spectate & auto-revive  
✅ Event mode: Solo / Squad  
✅ Anti-cheat basic & command protection  
✅ Optimized performance untuk 50+ pemain

---

